Package Constants

Class AppConstants

java.lang.Object
Constants.AppConstants
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AppConstants extends Object implements Serializable
This class defines a set of constants used throughout the application. These constants include error messages, command formats, file extensions, and color codes for console output.
Version:
3.0.0
Author:
Sumit Sharma, Muhammad Adnan Asad, Pranaykumar Chauhan, Darshansinh Dilipsinh Devda, Dhruvkumar Parmar, Dhruv Patel
